# Mobile App Collaboration Rule

- Build in phases and wait for user confirmation before starting the next phase.
- Explain updates in beginner format:
  - What changed
  - Why it changed
  - How to verify
- Prefer normal commands first.
- Avoid force flags/options unless blocked and no safer option works.
- Keep architecture clean and minimal; avoid unnecessary libraries.
